flowRoot.flowPara: FSFTN resource persons conduct 1 or 2 guest lectures on introduction to free software and key concepts, possibilities of contributing to free software, job prospects and the how to join and benefit from the start-up boom.
FSFTN organises both 2 and 3-day workshops. On varied topics like
File system Architecture and Shell Scripting
We normally prefer a 2 or 3 day-workshops , though it may also be scaled to 5 days depending upon the support from the institution and the number of participants.
Though we maintain the fees structure as 500/2 day session and 600/3 day session its negotiable based on the needs.
